Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?  在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能贏嗎  用你的玩具的話
